        *      @monthly - Run once a month, midnight, first of month - 0 0 1 * *
        *      @weekly - Run once a week, midnight on Sun - 0 0 * * 0
        *      @daily - Run once a day, midnight - 0 0 * * *
        *      @hourly - Run once an hour, first minute - 0 * * * *
